parameters: Finally! Humans! Been waiting to kill humans!
I look like human? Yes! Yes! Yes! I was. Not anymore! Die! Die! Die!
Yes! It was me who defeated Dyahc!
I'll be back in 5 years and destroy all your children!!!!
You have come this far... Only the Knight of Light can come
this far and I don't care if you are the Knight of Light. I can beat
you easily and feed your head to my slaves!!!
Some are already in my stomach! You can join them later, don't worry!
I thought Lucio is scary, I think we have found a clown.
Give us the people and we will not let you suffer!
Can I just keep him as a pet?
Enough! Show me what you've got!
You think you won? I'll be back... and no matter how many times
you kill me, I'll keep on coming back!!! Wahahahaha!
He can keep on coming back, and we can keep on beating him.
I just wish that our loved ones are still there.
My son! You came! Thank you!
I knew it, Babe! You'll come to save us!
Sorry! It took so long! You're safe now!
Shake!!! Thank God! Thank God! Thank God! I thought I lost you!
